							  readpkgelf
v0.0

Description:

    This is a simple tool to read archive files and print the required
    libraries of each contains ELF object file.

    More features may be added in the future.

Installation:

    Dependencies:

        built time:
            a C++11 compatible compiler
            llvm
            libarchive
            BSD or GNU compatible `make'
        runtime:
            libarchive

    Installation:

        run `make'
        There is no `make install' target yet.

